data.description: Charming well maintained brick ranch located close to everything.  Main level features large open kitchen-dining room area, living room, bath, and 2 bedrooms. In the basement you will find additional family room, work out area or possible gaming area, laundry room with 1/2 bath, and 2 storage rooms.  Home has original hard wood floors, updated kitchen which includes all new appliances new in 2020, in addition to washer, dryer, and freezer. Other updates include: 13 inches added attic insulation, new HVAC 2020, roof 2019, and basement waterproof 2019. Outside you will find a one + car detached garage, large area for parking on this partially wooded lot.  Average 12 month gas/electric $136.70. Contract with Swat pest.
